resources.string: 第1回 ガキの使いやあらへんで
Chiki Chiki Tube has no specific operating expenses, so don\'t worry about that! But other forms of support are possible:
- Provide feedback on broken links/bad metadata etc
- Typesetting interesting and funny episodes that have as yet been unsubbed!
- Submitting any new releases to The Silent Library ➚

- Setting up your own Peertube server ➚ and mirroring videos via redundancy from chikichiki.tube. This will seamlessly increase the bandwidth thanks to peer to peer magic. (N.B. Just following the instance with your server doesn\'t do much for that)
Metadata is from knightscoop.yabai.moe ➚ and ghia.chu.jp/wiki ➚
Have a look at some homemade comedy at wacast.net ➚
